      "content": "it just feels like the world kept moving but i didn't. everyone says \"it gets better\" or \"give it time\" but they don't get it. time is just more empty space. what's the point of even trying to fight it? everything that made life worth it is just... gone. i feel like i'm just waiting for something to happen so i don't have to feel this emptiness anymore.",
